msg: svn_path_canonicalize() wasn't removing trailing slashes on some URIs.
With help from Michael W Thelen and Arild Fines.
(svn_path_canonicalize): When canonicalizing a URI always remove the
trailing slash.  Also remove the unused start_path variable.
(text_canonicalize): All tests should result in a canonical path.
